BEGIN CAMPAIGN DOSSIER — B2h (Active Threats)
====================================================================
Master list of all active threats. Updated through Session 10.
Threats are listed in descending order of severity.

════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

THREAT: Charter Protocol (ARCHIVIST, CURATOR, SURGEON, JANITOR)
  Level: EXTREME
  Status: Active — Dr. Arisawa Defection Undiscovered
  Description: Shadowy black-ops bureau. Council confirmed: ARCHIVIST (AI), CURATOR, SURGEON, JANITOR. Anchor designated BLACK STAR.
  Intel: ARCHIVIST awaiting senior assessment of BLACK STAR designation. Timeline unknown. SURGEON actively hunting Sunspot Core. No known leads.
  Update: JANITOR submitted termination request for Anchor (Site Hydra aftermath) — [DENIED – PENDING SENIOR ASSESSMENT]. Reason for denial unknown. May be strategic patience, resource allocation, or something else.
  Contingency: "Cleansing Fire" remains in effect.

THREAT: Shiawase Corporation
  Level: EXTREME
  Status: Active
  Description: Megacorporation. Focused Enemy (-6).
  Losses: Helios Wing breached, Site Hydra lost, Dr. Elara Lian defected, prototype meta-asset (Stabilized Echo) acquired by Anchor.
  Action: Active black-ops pursuit. Director Hideo Yamato is a named antagonist.

THREAT: Yamatetsu
  Level: HIGH (ESCALATING)
  Status: Active — Breach Undiscovered
  Description: Megacorporation. Hostile (-3).
  Losses: Archive Theta (Sector 4G) breached. Priority-7 asset "Waking Stone" stolen. Sector 4G handler Dr. Arisawa defected.
  Intel: Breach undiscovered. ETA to discovery: 24-48 hours.
  Upon Discovery: Internal investigation → corporate security mobilization → asset recovery prioritization. Dr. Arisawa will be designated [DECEASED] or [TRAITOR]. No middle ground.

THREAT: The Sunspire Seedling
  Level: HIGH / ENTROPIC
  Status: Uncontained
  Description: A synthetic metaphysical entity, grown from refined ECHO BREACH resonance substrates.
  Location: Loose within Shiawase Atrium (Helios Wing and potentially beyond).
  Nature: Metastable. Form and consciousness in flux. Not malicious by default.
  Drives: Self-preservation, understanding of its own nature, consumption/assimilation of resonant energy.
  Weakness: Stability tied to ambient resonance. May be drawn to familiar signatures (Resonant Stone, Sunspot Core, Stabilized Echo).

THREAT: WYRM-SIGN
  Level: HIGH
  Status: Active
  Description: Consortium of free spirits and minor dragons. Aggressive (-3).
  Losses: Artifact (K-7 Whispering Shard) intercepted by Anchor.
  Action: Seeking recovery and/or retribution.

THREAT: Shotozumi-gumi (Yakuza)
  Level: HIGH (ESCALATED)
  Status: Active
  Description: Organized crime syndicate. Hostile (-5).
  Losses: Major sea shipment and high-value art/BTL consignment lost from their own Tacoma dock. Lieutenant Kaito Suzuki critically compromised.
  Status: Internal turmoil. Audits and reprisals certain.

THREAT: MCT Black-Ops
  Level: MEDIUM
  Status: Active
  Description: Corporate response level unknown from Site 3B conflict.
  Note: Has not been the primary focus of recent sessions, but remains a live thread.

THREAT: Schmidt-Krupp Biomedical
  Level: MEDIUM
  Status: Active (NEW)
  Description: Shiawase subsidiary. Hostile (-4).
  Losses: Black-site lab Site Hydra, researcher Dr. Elara Lian (defected), prototype meta-asset (Stabilized Echo).
  Action: Retainer payments to Moth Properties ceased. Internal audit in progress.

